text: Patricia Eachus née Keller (born 26 September 1989) is a Swiss Paralympic athlete who competes in middle-distance and long-distance racing events in international level events. ==References== Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:People from Sursee District Category:Paralympic athletes of Switzerland Category:Swiss female wheelchair racers Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2012 Summer Paralympics
